# ClickIRST: Towards Interactive Segmentation for Infrared Small Target


## Datasets
We used the WideIRSTD for both training and testing, SIRST3 only for testing.

### Commands for runing demo
```
python demo.py --checkpoint=experiments/ckick10/checkpoints/last_checkpoint.pth --gpu 0
```
  
### Commands for training
```
python train.py models/iter_mask/plainvit_huge448_cocolvis_itermask.py \
--batch-size=16 \
--gpus=0,1
```
### Commands for test
  ```
  python scripts/evaluate_model.py NoBRS --gpu=0 --checkpoint=experiments/ckick10/checkpoints/last_checkpoint.pth --eval-mode=cvpr --datasets=SIRST3
  ```
